Aug. 6, 2010
- enja.cpp : #include "opencl.cl" files (opencl code)
    update if adding new code. 

- If a new file is added, in enja.cpp, modify: 
    EnjaParticles::sources[] = {
        lorenz_program_source,
        gravity_program_source,
        vfield_program_source,
        collision_program_source,
        position_program_source
    };

- If a new kernel is added to one of these files, or a kernel name is changed, 
  modify lines such as: 

   collision_kernel = cl::Kernel(collision_program, "collision_ge", &err);

- 
